description: Tucker Vaughn has been having some trouble in a couple of his classes, and badly needs tutoring. Austin Wilde has had his eye on Tucker for quite a while, and has offered his services. Now, you could list everything Austin knows about microbiology on one side of  a matchbook cover, but that is neither here nor there. Because, truth be told, as soon as they get to Tucker's room, the only thing on Austin's mind is giving Tucker a long hard lesson in Cockology. Enjoy!
title: TUTOR MY ASS
